{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0e09a1d391","title":"随笔：无花的蔷薇","origin":"《武汉大学右派言论汇编》（中共武汉大学社会主义思想教育办公室，1957.12）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0d040a6a02","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"0e09a1d391"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"979f75cd2c","name":"卢斯飞"},{"id":"c504f98253","name":"武汉大学"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d4a81292c3","type":"title","text":"随笔：无花的蔷薇","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e09a1d391"},{"id":"d397e4d0a4","type":"authors","text":"武汉大学卢斯飞","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e09a1d391"},{"id":"fc66d4a034","type":"subtitle","text":"（卢斯飞：武汉大学中文系学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e09a1d391"},{"id":"c418d0dbc1","type":"paragraph","text":"张资琪、段桂棠先生，在肃反时被斗得不亦乐呼。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e09a1d391"},{"id":"2bb3a0b317","type":"paragraph","text":"张副校长说：这不是领导的错，是群众要搞的。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e09a1d391"},{"id":"f93f1829c1","type":"paragraph","text":"张、段两先生：你们沈默好几年了，（你们该还在这里吧？）群众请你们回答！","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e09a1d391"},{"id":"46c2777a7e","type":"paragraph","text":"×××","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e09a1d391"},{"id":"3e3d5c56a8","type":"paragraph","text":"因为外国代表团要参观武大，一批“老虎”被带到山上去避人耳目，他们是在肃反时期没有经过任何法律手续，被“集中”（！）起来的。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e09a1d391"},{"id":"871ac58ead","type":"paragraph","text":"真的不要躲，躲的不是真——在今天的光明世界而一九五五年正是宪法通过后的第一年。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e09a1d391"},{"id":"a508233767","type":"paragraph","text":"×××","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e09a1d391"},{"id":"1b32a83dc1","type":"paragraph","text":"我们全班都会积极参加肃反工作。被斗的人都是党委批准的；领导对我们说：材料充足，证据确凿，但是，我们斗错了，他们全是好人。现在，相信“领导”也得看什么人的领导。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e09a1d391"},{"id":"95844a34cd","type":"paragraph","text":"领导者谁？张副校长，张希光书记王勇副处长………也。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e09a1d391"},{"id":"079e915a5e","type":"paragraph","text":"×××","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e09a1d391"},{"id":"36e8386339","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反时期，动员人数百个，耗资五百万，天南地北，行迹十五省外出调查材材。保管这些材料的人是人事处；增加材料的也是人事处。根据现在情况看，过去有不少人受过冤枉诬陷。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e09a1d391"},{"id":"13337d6e56","type":"paragraph","text":"为了避免以后再有人含冤莫白，欲告无门，人事处应在同学毕业前，把材料让每人看一次。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e09a1d391"},{"id":"9dc8f3ea08","type":"paragraph","text":"是真的就不怕人看！","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e09a1d391"},{"id":"5f5eafc29b","type":"paragraph","text":"×××","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e09a1d391"},{"id":"143de32853","type":"paragraph","text":"毕业论文两次被指导老师评为二分的人，可以留为本系助教，为什么？她是党员。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e09a1d391"},{"id":"b2e4aefd69","type":"paragraph","text":"一个读了三年书的人把自己分配到作家协会工作，业务比他好得多的人都分配到初中教书。为什么？前者是肃反组，党员，后者是普通同学。党员！团员！多少人伪尔之名，行见不得人之事！","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e09a1d391"},{"id":"ed8ae13885","type":"paragraph","text":"×××","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e09a1d391"},{"id":"93dd81defb","type":"paragraph","text":"张斌说：我把这党员让给你当啦！说得好！“让”“当”二字太妙！张斌同志说得多自然，多有分寸！在某些人看来，党员是一个官卫，入党，是为了党官；当官的人岂可挨批评？怪不得他要吹胡子瞪眼睛连“党员”也要让给人当了。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e09a1d391"},{"id":"7551cc1be0","type":"paragraph","text":"×××","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e09a1d391"},{"id":"165460798a","type":"paragraph","text":"因为属意某人的妹妹，他可以为某人晋级；一位不愿呆在武汉的女同志，他总要勉强她留在科内。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e09a1d391"},{"id":"f249973462","type":"paragraph","text":"他是谁？——人事科叶副科长。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e09a1d391"},{"id":"76a2ccba41","type":"paragraph","text":"但是，一个大学生直到离校前一天晚上，才知道学了四年的前途怎样，发通知书的是谁？人事处的官员们。","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e09a1d391"},{"id":"9f38508bf5","type":"paragraph","text":"掌握我们命运的人是怎样的人啊！","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e09a1d391"}],"page":{"id":"1b5d379bc6","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e09a1d391","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}